{"tid":2286924,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警拘捕23歲男子 指他與民建聯女子起爭執後被不禮貌拍攝 繼而動粗致對方手部紅了","createTime":"2020-11-15T11:19:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T11:58:12.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e725c28ef9ba085ce947ce01ba64cd6167c73f51","tid":2286924,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T11:19:53.000Z","msg":"警拘捕23歲男子 涉天水圍襲擊民建聯女成員<br />\n<br />\n一名23歲男子涉嫌普通襲擊被捕。事發在昨日早上11時許，民建聯在天水圍天耀邨擺街站收集簽名，支持中央及特區政府取消4名立法會議員資格，警方指，23歲男子期間因政見問題，與一名47歲民建聯女成員爭執，女成員用手機拍攝男子時，男子用手推開她，然後逃去。民建聯女成員報稱手部紅腫。警方調查後，下午在天水圍區拘捕涉案男子，他正被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2366367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2366367&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BM3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=7c3a00a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2366367</a>"},{"pid":"7f6b9e3827bc6f3c5f1965dfd9a7ec8a61ca3496","tid":2286924,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T11:27:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"196ca71ad67c83264c6a78fbf8c4ff29d5c70549","tid":2286924,"uid":35930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T11:29:04.000Z","msg":"不提證供起訴"},{"pid":"3da0b4727c41d18fe14f4855d21cc246a4039f61","tid":2286924,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T11:33:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"029b4e3eb65d6903d5cd825bc844fd88d2bae519","tid":2286924,"uid":167928,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T11:33:53.000Z","msg":"認真 咪聽連登仔鳩up獅鳥藍絲 <br />\n切勿衝動"}